Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.89,0:01:22.06,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}暗夜的乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.38,0:01:23.80,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}嘘か夢か
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.38,0:01:23.80,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是梦是幻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.17,0:01:25.80,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}失うのは身体と
