Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.17,0:01:25.80,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}失去的是身体
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.87,0:01:27.37,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}自分という心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.87,0:01:27.37,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}和自我之心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.46,0:01:29.16,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}その対価を差し出し
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.46,0:01:29.16,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}付出如此代价
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.26,0:01:32.23,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}何を得られるのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.26,0:01:32.23,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}又能得到什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.43,0:01:35.99,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}この涙で奪える程に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.43,0:01:35.99,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}连这泪水都能将之夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.16,0:01:39.31,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}命は脆くて儚くて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.16,0:01:39.31,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}生命脆弱而飘忽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.40,0:01:42.78,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}全てに訪れる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.40,0:01:42.78,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}当一切造访
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.93,0:01:46.11,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}死を「恐怖」と嘆くのか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.93,0:01:46.11,OP-ED-JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\fs14\pos(235,330)}終わり
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.93,0:01:46.11,OP-ED-Ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}要将死亡叹作恐怖吗
